data.description: Ready to move in home. The Kitchen features SS appliances, a Kitchen island with a snack bar, and a large pantry. The bathrooms were remodeled. Very Functional floor plan with family room and dining room separate from the kitchen. The living room, Master bedroom, and family room are open to the Pool patio area with a pool heater, central vacuum, and a new 5-ton A.C. Oversized Corner lot on a quiet street with space for a boat or RV. Cypress Creek is a 24/7 manned gated community of custom build homes on full-size lots. All pets are welcome any size or breed no restrictions.
